WEBVTT

01:38.240 --> 01:40.600
EPISODE 21

01:54.560 --> 01:58.080
IDEAS FOR THE HOME SYSTEM

02:02.600 --> 02:05.760
New gameplays for spirit monsters.

02:09.240 --> 02:12.840
Oh, yeah! I haven't fed my tiger in days.

02:28.520 --> 02:31.920
Sorry, I've been too busy.
I forgot about you.

02:32.920 --> 02:36.200
Lord's tiger probably
hasn't been fed in days, either.

02:39.560 --> 02:41.240
I'll go get some food.

02:41.320 --> 02:44.320
Stay here and look after the house.
Don't run off!

02:46.120 --> 02:49.160
Why does this sound a bit familiar?

02:52.080 --> 02:54.480
Then look after the house.
Don't go to Xiaoling's.

03:05.760 --> 03:06.800
Diemeng?

03:11.240 --> 03:12.320
Weiwei?

03:14.280 --> 03:15.440
Here you are, Weiwei!

03:17.520 --> 03:20.160
You're here, too, Nini?
What a coincidence.

03:20.240 --> 03:21.080
I haven't seen you in ages.

03:23.080 --> 03:23.960
Work's been crazy.

03:24.760 --> 03:27.600
Weiwei, you've been gone for ages, too,
not just Diemeng.

03:29.400 --> 03:32.240
Yes, I've been busy with work, too.

03:32.320 --> 03:33.600
I've been interning.

03:35.040 --> 03:36.640
I guess I'm the only idle one.

03:37.680 --> 03:39.560
It's rare for us three to get together.

03:39.640 --> 03:41.320
Why don't we go to an instance dungeon?

03:43.360 --> 03:44.240
Sure.

03:44.960 --> 03:48.160
I haven't played in a while.
My maneuvering might be rusty.

03:48.800 --> 03:52.080
It's okay. Let's warm up
with average difficulty.

03:52.160 --> 03:54.720
Weiwei's here. I'm sure we'll crack it.

04:16.560 --> 04:17.519
Watch out!

04:24.080 --> 04:26.920
Two months offline,
and I forgot how to kill a boss.

04:27.000 --> 04:29.000
I'll go visit an NPC and fix my equipment.

04:33.800 --> 04:36.000
Clan Leader Diemeng has been moody.

04:36.600 --> 04:37.720
What's wrong?

04:39.120 --> 04:41.480
Maybe she's not used to the clan anymore.

04:41.560 --> 04:44.080
Many old faces have left
in the past two months.

04:44.160 --> 04:47.440
A lot of new clan members
idolize Xiaoyu Yaoyao.

04:47.520 --> 04:49.920
Many don't even know Clan Leader Diemeng.

04:51.000 --> 04:53.520
Zhan Tianxia didn't give her back
the leadership?

04:54.440 --> 04:55.400
No.

04:55.480 --> 04:58.120
Now, Clan Leader Diemeng's grade
and progression

04:58.200 --> 04:59.960
aren't as high as Zhan Tianxia's.

05:00.040 --> 05:01.680
Xiaoyu Qingqing is still in the clan.

05:01.760 --> 05:02.920
That woman is so hateful.

05:03.480 --> 05:06.080
If I weren't so attached to the clan,
I'd have left.

05:08.760 --> 05:11.120
Diemeng and Zhan Tianxia...

05:11.720 --> 05:14.480
They made up. I asked Clan Leader Diemeng.

05:14.560 --> 05:16.120
She said she fell ill a while ago.

05:16.200 --> 05:18.800
Zhan Tianxia took care of her,
so she forgave him.

05:18.880 --> 05:20.760
Let's leave it. Diemeng is back.

05:23.320 --> 05:24.160
Shall we continue?

05:25.080 --> 05:28.360
No, my internet isn't stable.
I keep getting kicked off.

05:28.440 --> 05:29.560
Let's just chat.

05:30.280 --> 05:33.960
Weiwei, you said
you have an internship. Where?

05:34.560 --> 05:35.520
In Capital City.

05:37.320 --> 05:41.000
You're studious. You're back
for your internship during summer break.

05:44.600 --> 05:45.600
I guess so.

05:47.320 --> 05:48.360
You're in Capital City, Weiwei?

05:51.200 --> 05:52.040
Yes.

05:52.920 --> 05:56.520
Are you free now?
Why don't we grab a coffee?

05:57.440 --> 06:01.240
Go ahead. It's so awesome
you're in the same city.

06:01.320 --> 06:03.480
I wish were in Capital City, too.

06:05.400 --> 06:07.960
Sure, where shall we meet?

06:08.800 --> 06:10.160
Are you in University District?

06:12.240 --> 06:13.200
That's right.

06:14.520 --> 06:17.040
There's a cafe named Red
on University Road.

06:17.120 --> 06:18.080
Shall we meet there?

06:21.880 --> 06:22.720
Sure.

06:26.360 --> 06:28.680
I'm wearing a dark green dress
and a white shirt.

06:28.760 --> 06:30.960
My cell phone number is 196...

06:39.840 --> 06:40.680
Weiwei?

06:49.320 --> 06:50.400
Lord?

06:54.320 --> 06:55.160
Yes.

06:57.760 --> 06:59.840
Can't you use
a regular message app to chat?

07:02.680 --> 07:03.800
This is convenient.

07:05.520 --> 07:07.560
It's scary, okay?

07:10.160 --> 07:12.960
I just recalled, my relatives
aren't staying in their villa now.

07:15.760 --> 07:16.640
What?

07:17.400 --> 07:20.600
They have a pool.
Do you want to go swimming?

07:21.440 --> 07:23.560
The missus needs to build up
health and strength.

07:27.280 --> 07:28.520
Swimming?

07:30.040 --> 07:33.280
Say, Xiao Nai is a better swimmer
than basketball player.

07:33.360 --> 07:37.040
I wonder what he looks like
during a swim meet?

07:39.440 --> 07:40.280
Yes.

07:42.720 --> 07:43.880
Can you swim?

07:46.560 --> 07:48.480
No, but I can watch.

07:56.920 --> 08:00.480
By the way, I'm meeting up with
Diemeng in a bit.

08:05.880 --> 08:07.080
Diemeng Weixing?

08:09.640 --> 08:12.280
Yes, she wants to meet and chat,

08:12.440 --> 08:15.120
at the cafe named Red, on University Road.

08:15.200 --> 08:17.520
We're just meeting for coffee.
It won't take long.

08:17.880 --> 08:20.960
I'll pick you up and take you swimming.

08:22.360 --> 08:25.600
By the way, bring my swimming trunks.

08:26.040 --> 08:27.280
They're at the bottom of the closet.

08:27.960 --> 08:29.440
Swimming trunks?

08:55.160 --> 08:56.000
Weiwei?

09:04.400 --> 09:05.360
Got it.

09:31.000 --> 09:32.840
We've all worked overtime for two days.

09:32.960 --> 09:34.400
Go home and get some rest.

09:34.680 --> 09:36.640
Relax a bit. You'll be more efficient.

09:37.480 --> 09:38.760
What's going on?

09:38.840 --> 09:40.600
- Really? Sure!
- For real?

09:40.680 --> 09:42.320
- Awesome!
- This is great!

09:42.400 --> 09:43.240
It's mandatory.

09:43.960 --> 09:45.440
Fantastic!

09:45.520 --> 09:47.560
- Okay.
- Grab your stuff. Now!

09:47.640 --> 09:49.960
Let's try that grilled scallop place, K.O.

09:50.040 --> 09:51.240
Maybe you can steal their recipe.

09:54.040 --> 09:55.480
Where are you off to, Nai?

09:55.840 --> 09:56.680
Swimming.

09:57.520 --> 10:00.080
- Take me with.
- It's not appropriate.

10:01.040 --> 10:02.200
Not appropriate?

10:02.280 --> 10:04.320
- I'm taking off. Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye, Nai!

10:36.120 --> 10:39.480
White shirt, dark green dress.

10:45.680 --> 10:46.760
Hello.

10:50.440 --> 10:52.720
You're Luwei Weiwei?

10:54.360 --> 10:55.640
Hi, Diemeng.

10:56.800 --> 10:58.600
Are you really Luwei Weiwei?

11:00.120 --> 11:00.960
I am.

11:03.200 --> 11:06.280
I'm sorry, I didn't expect you
to be so pretty in person.

11:07.760 --> 11:09.280
Have a seat.

11:15.960 --> 11:19.080
What would you like to drink? Server!

11:22.800 --> 11:24.360
Hi, what can I get for you?

11:25.080 --> 11:27.400
- A milk tea.
- Okay, just a moment.

11:30.720 --> 11:34.280
Weiwei, I never expected
you'd be so pretty in real life.

11:35.240 --> 11:36.880
I'm so surprised.

11:37.040 --> 11:39.840
The Xiaoyus are always spreading rumors,

11:40.760 --> 11:43.920
that you're either ugly
or a bio-man in disguise.

11:45.560 --> 11:48.680
If they saw you in person,
they'd be so ashamed.

11:49.760 --> 11:53.360
And that Zhenshui Wuxiang,
he has zero taste.

11:53.440 --> 11:55.520
If he saw you in person,
he'd kick himself.

11:57.160 --> 11:59.280
Diemeng, let's not talk about the others.

12:01.600 --> 12:04.480
Look at me, we finally meet in person,

12:04.560 --> 12:06.600
and I brought up all that past.

12:07.040 --> 12:08.400
You must be upset.

12:09.560 --> 12:11.200
I'm not upset.

12:12.120 --> 12:15.960
To me, he's just like any other stranger.

12:17.520 --> 12:20.480
It's amazing you can let it go like that.

12:22.480 --> 12:26.040
Unlike me. I can never let it go.

12:26.880 --> 12:28.920
Because of Xiaoyu Qingqing,

12:29.080 --> 12:31.280
I was ready to break up
with Zhan Tianxia.

12:32.000 --> 12:36.480
But then, he was so good to me again,
all of a sudden.

12:39.360 --> 12:41.360
I fell ill for a while.

12:41.800 --> 12:46.200
He was always running around,
taking care of me, and staying with me.

12:48.240 --> 12:49.880
So we made up.

12:50.840 --> 12:54.680
That's good. I'm happy for you.

12:57.520 --> 12:59.320
It's not what you think.

13:00.240 --> 13:02.000
I only realize now,

13:05.080 --> 13:07.160
a relationship that's gone sour,

13:07.760 --> 13:10.920
is the same as food that's turned bad.

13:12.000 --> 13:14.240
You can't keep it. You have to toss it.

13:15.440 --> 13:17.440
We may be back together,

13:18.680 --> 13:21.840
but our feelings are never the same.

13:22.520 --> 13:24.960
He thinks that I forgave him once,

13:25.440 --> 13:28.160
I can forgive him a second time,
a third time.

13:30.560 --> 13:32.680
So he's gotten worse.

13:36.280 --> 13:37.200
Weiwei...

13:41.600 --> 13:43.120
I'm so tired.

13:47.080 --> 13:50.520
Don't be sad, Diemeng.

14:29.480 --> 14:32.040
I feel much better now,
having talked to you.

14:32.120 --> 14:34.800
Why don't we have dinner later?
What do you think?

14:39.200 --> 14:43.280
Sorry, I have plans tonight.
I'm learning to swim.

14:45.480 --> 14:46.320
With your boyfriend?

14:49.600 --> 14:51.560
You're so beautiful.

14:51.640 --> 14:54.800
Your boyfriend must be devoted to you.

14:57.360 --> 14:59.640
Since you already have plans,
I won't keep you.

14:59.880 --> 15:02.080
Go ahead,
I want to sit for a while longer.

15:02.160 --> 15:03.040
It's my treat today.

15:03.640 --> 15:05.960
It's okay. I'll pay for it myself.

15:06.440 --> 15:07.920
Don't be so formal with me.

15:08.000 --> 15:10.360
I'm working already.
You're still a student.

15:10.440 --> 15:11.280
It's okay.

15:12.320 --> 15:17.120
Well, thank you. Next time, it's my treat.

15:17.480 --> 15:18.320
Okay.

15:24.480 --> 15:25.680
WEIWEI

15:30.600 --> 15:32.360
Hello? I'm done.

15:33.480 --> 15:35.280
Okay, I'll be right there.

15:36.280 --> 15:38.680
I'll wait outside the cafe.

15:39.440 --> 15:40.360
Okay.

15:42.400 --> 15:43.280
Have you bought a swimsuit?

15:46.640 --> 15:47.640
Want me to go with you?

15:50.920 --> 15:53.640
Let's go shopping together. I see you now.

15:55.920 --> 15:57.040
Don't do that!

15:57.120 --> 15:58.760
There's a shop nearby. I'll go myself.

16:12.520 --> 16:15.360
- Are you looking for a swimsuit?
- Yes.

16:15.560 --> 16:18.800
You have a great figure.
These are perfect for you.

16:21.000 --> 16:22.200
No, thanks.

16:40.720 --> 16:42.840
You got it? That was fast.

16:44.200 --> 16:45.080
I knew I had to be.

16:48.960 --> 16:52.920
I bought the swimsuit,
but I don't have to wear it.

16:53.080 --> 16:56.200
I won't get in the water.
What can you do? Pull me in?

17:55.560 --> 17:57.640
I can take pictures on my phone, too.

17:57.920 --> 18:00.680
My plan is perfect.

18:35.680 --> 18:36.720
Get changed first.

18:43.960 --> 18:45.000
Where are my swim trunks?

18:54.880 --> 18:55.840
Why did you pick these?

18:58.120 --> 19:00.360
What's wrong with those?

19:01.160 --> 19:05.400
My aunt bought me these after I won
the inter-school swimming championship.

19:05.480 --> 19:06.480
I've never worn these.

19:08.080 --> 19:08.920
You don't like them?

19:11.440 --> 19:12.360
I don't mind them.

19:14.480 --> 19:17.520
I just never thought...

19:18.400 --> 19:20.480
you'd be into this style.

19:29.280 --> 19:31.000
What style?

20:03.960 --> 20:05.880
The short and skinny kind?

20:05.960 --> 20:07.680
I got the revealing swim trunks?

20:07.760 --> 20:11.160
If I say I grabbed them by accident,
will he believe me?

20:24.720 --> 20:28.400
Wasn't I only going to watch?
Why did I come in to change?

21:01.360 --> 21:02.280
Hello, Xiaomeng?

21:03.120 --> 21:04.280
Tianxia,

21:06.440 --> 21:08.080
it's dinner time.

21:08.160 --> 21:10.520
Do you want to meet for dinner?

21:10.800 --> 21:12.480
I know a good steakhouse.

21:12.800 --> 21:15.480
No, I'm meeting people
in an instance dungeon.

21:15.560 --> 21:16.400
It'll take a while.

21:18.280 --> 21:19.400
Meeting whom?

21:20.520 --> 21:24.280
Just some people from the clan.

21:24.360 --> 21:27.160
As the clan leader,
I have to contribute my time, no?

21:29.480 --> 21:30.320
All right.

21:37.440 --> 21:40.800
It's been forever, but you haven't
helped me reach Frozen Prison.

21:42.880 --> 21:44.720
All right. I'll keep working on it.

21:47.480 --> 21:48.760
That's more like it.

21:48.840 --> 21:51.960
But, would Ms. Diemeng get mad,
if she found out?

21:52.280 --> 21:53.840
It's fine, we're all in the clan.

21:54.160 --> 21:55.760
You girls might have a hard time.

21:55.840 --> 21:57.280
As the clan leader, I must help.

21:58.120 --> 22:01.280
You're going to an instance dungeon?
Do you want my help?

22:02.920 --> 22:03.920
What are you doing here, Diemeng?

22:05.200 --> 22:06.320
I shouldn't be here?

22:06.400 --> 22:08.840
You said you're helping the clan
with an instance dungeon, no?

22:09.080 --> 22:11.320
As the former clan leader,

22:11.400 --> 22:12.960
I came to offer my help.

22:17.080 --> 22:18.960
It's best if Ms. Diemeng can help.

22:21.200 --> 22:23.320
For this instance dungeon,
as Tianxia said,

22:23.400 --> 22:25.600
you girls may have a hard time.

22:25.680 --> 22:27.480
Helping out is no big deal.

22:27.960 --> 22:31.080
But, I had an eye-opener today.

22:33.160 --> 22:34.120
What?

22:34.720 --> 22:36.440
I met up with Luwei Weiwei today.

22:39.040 --> 22:40.240
You met Luwei Weiwei?

22:40.800 --> 22:43.880
Yes, she's a stunner in person.

22:44.080 --> 22:47.960
If she was on a reality TV show,
perhaps...

22:52.440 --> 22:55.040
Luwei Weiwei? How's that possible?

22:56.960 --> 22:58.400
Well, believe it or not, it's up to you.

23:15.960 --> 23:18.480
Diemeng made a bluff
in front of Zhan Tianxia,

23:18.560 --> 23:21.440
saying Luwei Weiwei is a stunner.
It's ridiculous.

23:21.680 --> 23:23.840
The whole server knows
she's a hag, okay?

23:23.920 --> 23:26.800
Right? Why make up a lie like that?

23:26.880 --> 23:28.360
That's just crazy.

23:29.080 --> 23:32.400
Do you think Ms. Diemeng
has a misunderstanding with us?

23:32.480 --> 23:36.360
I don't think so. She's just jealous
Tianxia cares about me.

23:37.480 --> 23:41.160
Qingqing, what's the nature
of your relationship with Zhan Tianxia?

23:41.600 --> 23:45.200
What relationship? We're totally innocent.

23:45.280 --> 23:47.480
He only helps me kill enemies
and get equipment.

23:48.040 --> 23:50.720
Diemeng thinks he's great,
but he means nothing to me.

23:51.880 --> 23:53.600
She's worried no one wants her?

23:56.080 --> 23:59.560
By the way, Yaoyao, didn't Zhenshui say

23:59.640 --> 24:02.120
Luwei Weiwei is interning at his company?

24:04.040 --> 24:06.840
I bet Diemeng never expected this,
when she made up that lie.

24:08.680 --> 24:12.360
Yaoyao, ask Zhenshui
to take us to his workplace.

24:12.960 --> 24:15.480
Let's go see what Luwei Weiwei looks like.

24:16.960 --> 24:19.680
Is that a good idea?
I don't want Zhenshui to get suspicious.

24:20.040 --> 24:22.520
Why isn't it a good idea?
You two are dating.

24:22.600 --> 24:24.680
It's normal to want to see his workplace.

24:25.320 --> 24:27.720
Right? Zhenshui should take you.

24:27.800 --> 24:29.840
Otherwise, he's not serious about you.

24:31.320 --> 24:33.720
Well, I'll ask him.

24:47.840 --> 24:49.120
- Is it okay?
- Yes.

24:50.440 --> 24:51.280
Here.

25:03.360 --> 25:05.800
Shaoxiang,
has work been stressing you out?

25:06.040 --> 25:08.120
No, there's nothing big going on,

25:08.200 --> 25:09.320
just some minor stuff.

25:10.200 --> 25:12.120
If only I could help you.

25:14.320 --> 25:16.720
When will you take me
to see your workplace?

25:17.920 --> 25:19.000
Why do you want to see my workplace?

25:19.960 --> 25:21.680
We've been dating for so long,

25:21.760 --> 25:23.680
but you've never taken me
to your workplace.

25:25.640 --> 25:28.120
Please? I just want to take a look.

25:28.440 --> 25:30.240
If I were the boss, I'd say sure,

25:30.720 --> 25:33.400
but my dad is the boss. It's not up to me.

25:33.480 --> 25:36.520
I'll only take a look,
so I can know more about you,

25:36.600 --> 25:39.400
and what kind of people you work with.

25:39.480 --> 25:41.680
- Pretty please?
- Yuyao.

25:49.440 --> 25:52.200
Fine. I'll make arrangements. Okay?

25:52.320 --> 25:54.040
Really? That's great!

25:54.360 --> 25:55.200
Let's eat.

26:06.440 --> 26:07.640
Hi, Mr. Zhen.

26:31.240 --> 26:32.080
Hello?

26:32.560 --> 26:35.320
What? The young master
brought girls to the office?

26:35.600 --> 26:38.080
I think it's the young master's
real girlfriend.

26:39.000 --> 26:40.640
Real girlfriend?

26:40.800 --> 26:42.640
They came in holding hands.

26:42.720 --> 26:44.960
What about the one in general affairs?

26:45.560 --> 26:46.760
Who knows?

26:54.960 --> 26:56.080
Hi, Mr. Zhen.

27:04.120 --> 27:05.720
- It's huge!
- Awesome.

27:05.800 --> 27:07.120
Why have they come?

27:09.480 --> 27:11.800
They insisted. I couldn't say no.

27:13.880 --> 27:15.520
Did I do something wrong?

27:16.920 --> 27:18.120
No, it's fine.

27:20.040 --> 27:22.840
Zhenshui, your family is so wealthy.

27:23.440 --> 27:25.520
We're okay. Sit here.

27:25.600 --> 27:26.800
I'll treat you to a big meal tonight.

27:28.640 --> 27:31.240
Didn't you say Luwei Weiwei works here?

27:31.640 --> 27:32.480
Yes.

27:33.280 --> 27:35.160
Can we go see what she looks like?

27:37.480 --> 27:40.080
No, I don't want her to know I'm Zhenshui.

27:41.320 --> 27:43.000
We would never tell her.

27:43.080 --> 27:45.000
We only want to see what she looks like.

27:48.320 --> 27:50.080
Don't trouble Zhenshui all the time.

27:52.600 --> 27:53.560
It's okay. It's no trouble.

27:54.240 --> 27:57.400
- You can see her, but don't say anything.
- Okay.

28:00.800 --> 28:01.800
You...

28:04.040 --> 28:06.480
You're in HR, in charge of interns?

28:07.160 --> 28:09.160
Yes, Mr. Zhen. How can I help you?

28:09.240 --> 28:11.920
I remember you hired an intern
named Zhao Erxi.

28:12.000 --> 28:14.880
- Have her tend to the guests.
- Okay.

28:24.480 --> 28:25.320
Hello, Dad?

28:27.640 --> 28:29.600
Yes, I'm showing friends
around the office.

28:31.400 --> 28:33.240
Sure, I'll be right there.

28:35.520 --> 28:37.200
My dad wants to see me. I'll be back.

28:37.760 --> 28:40.800
- Okay, we'll wait here.
- Sure.

28:44.720 --> 28:48.200
Yaoyao, Zhenshui's family is loaded.

28:48.360 --> 28:51.440
It's a huge company. I looked it up.

28:51.520 --> 28:52.880
It's publicly traded.

28:53.480 --> 28:55.760
You're so lucky, Yaoyao,
for netting this one.

28:57.560 --> 28:59.440
That's not why I'm with him.

29:03.120 --> 29:06.000
- Mr. Zhen isn't here?
- His dad called him away.

29:06.880 --> 29:08.400
This is our intern, Zhao Erxi.

29:08.480 --> 29:11.160
Mr. Zhen asked her to tend to the guests.

29:11.440 --> 29:13.240
Erxi, tend to the guests here.

29:13.320 --> 29:15.440
- I'll get back to work. Bye.
- Okay.

29:17.920 --> 29:20.560
Hello, Mr. Zhen asked me to tend to you.

29:20.640 --> 29:22.360
Let me know, if you need anything.

29:24.440 --> 29:25.280
That's her?

29:28.760 --> 29:30.480
We're Mr. Zhen's friends.

29:30.560 --> 29:33.160
Why don't you get some coffee for us?

29:33.240 --> 29:35.880
- We'll wait for him here.
- I'll be back.

29:41.800 --> 29:43.640
This is what Diemeng called a stunner?

29:43.720 --> 29:45.880
What a joke!

29:46.200 --> 29:48.520
This is a crazy big bluff.

29:49.000 --> 29:50.320
I want to take a picture.

29:50.400 --> 29:52.600
Expose Diemeng's lie for all to see.

29:52.680 --> 29:55.160
No, Zhenshui would get mad.

29:55.520 --> 29:58.240
I know. I was just saying.

29:58.560 --> 30:02.000
Poor Zhenshui,
his former in-game spouse is so hideous.

30:02.520 --> 30:04.280
However pretty his new wife is,

30:04.360 --> 30:06.680
that's still a smear on his record.

30:13.480 --> 30:14.800
Here's your coffee.

30:27.800 --> 30:30.280
Give me my phone! Give it...

30:33.440 --> 30:35.920
My new shoes!

30:36.160 --> 30:40.000
I can't blow up at the manager's guests.
Suck it up.

30:41.480 --> 30:43.840
I'm so sorry. That was clumsy of me.

30:44.440 --> 30:45.880
I... I'm fine.

30:46.840 --> 30:48.000
Get me another cup.

30:51.960 --> 30:53.000
I'll swallow my pride.

30:53.720 --> 30:54.720
Okay.

31:05.200 --> 31:07.840
My coffee's cold. Get me a new cup.

31:07.920 --> 31:09.160
Sure.

31:11.040 --> 31:11.880
My ear stud!

31:12.640 --> 31:14.800
Did it fall under the sofa?

31:14.880 --> 31:16.160
What now?

31:16.720 --> 31:18.760
The pair you bought yesterday,
for three grand?

31:19.160 --> 31:20.000
Yes.

31:21.680 --> 31:23.880
Can you get it for me?

31:24.640 --> 31:26.600
We're all in skirts.

31:29.600 --> 31:30.600
Okay.

31:34.840 --> 31:36.640
What does it look like?

31:36.960 --> 31:40.120
It's a Tahiti black pearl, very expensive.

31:56.360 --> 31:57.800
I got it.

32:02.880 --> 32:05.600
- Is this it?
- Thanks.

32:39.120 --> 32:42.400
- Zhao Erxi?
- Mr. Zhen.

32:42.920 --> 32:44.280
Why do you look so battered?

32:44.720 --> 32:46.240
I'm getting stuff for them.

32:46.320 --> 32:48.960
Right, Mr. Zhen,
please give them the charger.

32:49.040 --> 32:52.080
Let me take a breather.
Call me, if you need me.

33:05.240 --> 33:06.520
Here's your charger.

33:09.840 --> 33:15.320
Zhenshui, Qingqing accidentally
spilled coffee on Luwei Weiwei's shoe.

33:15.600 --> 33:17.560
Do you think she's mad?

33:18.120 --> 33:20.560
She looked so scary just now.

33:21.400 --> 33:24.160
I thought she'd hit me, like in the game.

33:25.680 --> 33:28.880
Don't be scared.
She's just a lowly employee here.

33:29.080 --> 33:29.920
She'd never blow up at you.

33:31.760 --> 33:33.440
I knew you'd protect me.

33:43.920 --> 33:45.040
Goodbye for now.

33:45.120 --> 33:47.560
I'll take you out to dinner. Be good.

33:48.960 --> 33:49.800
See you.

33:50.200 --> 33:51.480
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

33:57.000 --> 33:58.840
I knew Diemeng was lying.

33:59.520 --> 34:01.600
Too bad we can't expose her.

34:02.120 --> 34:03.320
Says who?

34:03.680 --> 34:05.400
I've got an idea, Yaoyao.

34:06.400 --> 34:09.159
Let's ask Zhan Tianxia to hold
a get-together.

34:09.239 --> 34:11.560
Get Diemeng to invite Luwei Weiwei.

34:11.760 --> 34:13.960
Didn't she say Luwei Weiwei is a stunner?

34:15.400 --> 34:17.440
When everyone comes...

34:25.679 --> 34:27.280
I called this meeting

34:27.520 --> 34:29.480
to discuss a idea with you.

34:30.920 --> 34:31.760
What is it?

34:33.040 --> 34:34.800
Our clan has been around for a while,

34:34.880 --> 34:37.679
but interaction among members is lacking.

34:38.000 --> 34:39.159
So, I suggest,

34:39.360 --> 34:42.159
we organize a regional get-together
for the clan.

34:43.080 --> 34:45.239
You mean a players' meet-up?

34:45.840 --> 34:48.159
Yes, what do you think?

34:49.280 --> 34:50.960
- It's a great idea.
- Yes.

34:51.040 --> 34:51.880
I think it's good.

34:52.280 --> 34:53.679
We can eat and sing karaoke.

34:54.239 --> 34:55.639
If we can find an internet cafe

34:55.719 --> 34:56.920
and play online together,

34:57.560 --> 34:59.920
or have a celebration in the game,

35:00.240 --> 35:01.480
it'd be super fun.

35:01.840 --> 35:03.480
That sounds so exciting.

35:04.480 --> 35:07.480
Sure, but where should we meet?

35:07.560 --> 35:10.480
We're spread out everywhere.

35:11.000 --> 35:13.000
The server's called Capital City Bests.

35:13.080 --> 35:15.120
Most people are in Capital City, right?

35:15.200 --> 35:16.560
Let's hold the first meet-up
in Capital City?

35:17.280 --> 35:20.240
Sure, I'm in Capital City. Let's do this.

35:20.720 --> 35:22.760
- I'm so excited.
- I'm in Capital City, too.

35:22.840 --> 35:25.040
I've been hoping for this kind of event.

35:25.120 --> 35:26.080
Fantastic!

35:26.160 --> 35:28.520
Clan Leader, let's do this then.

35:28.960 --> 35:31.960
I'm not there.
I envy those of you in Capital City.

35:33.480 --> 35:35.680
It sounds like fun.

35:35.920 --> 35:39.560
- Should we go, Zhenshui?
- Sure. It should be fun.

35:40.040 --> 35:43.120
But, there will be so many people.

35:44.920 --> 35:47.240
So? You have nothing to hide.

35:48.040 --> 35:49.640
Okay, I'll do as you say.

35:51.680 --> 35:54.000
I like Tianxia's proposal.

35:54.080 --> 35:55.360
To show my support,

35:56.000 --> 35:58.200
I'll pay all the expenses
for this meet-up.

36:01.160 --> 36:04.680
- That's generous!
- Money's no issue for you, Zhenshui.

36:05.120 --> 36:07.920
- Even if we have a seafood feast?
- Sure.

36:08.840 --> 36:11.120
Okay, since everyone's onboard,

36:11.200 --> 36:12.600
let's organize this event.

36:13.800 --> 36:16.920
Diemeng, didn't you meet up
with Luwei Weiwei?

36:17.560 --> 36:18.760
Invite her, too.

36:19.120 --> 36:19.960
Luwei?

36:22.200 --> 36:24.680
Yes, there was a lot of misunderstanding.

36:24.760 --> 36:26.520
We can meet and talk things out.

36:31.280 --> 36:33.960
That's right.
It'd be best if she could come.

36:34.120 --> 36:36.480
We had our differences in the game,

36:36.800 --> 36:39.760
but it's just a game.
Real life is different.

36:40.600 --> 36:41.920
Didn't Ms. Diemeng say,

36:42.000 --> 36:44.360
Luwei is very pretty? I'm curious.

36:49.200 --> 36:51.400
Really? Luwei is a beauty?

36:51.480 --> 36:54.200
I thought she was a bio-man in disguise.
I want to meet up! I want photos!

36:55.080 --> 36:57.760
Princess Butterfly,
you're in charge of this great mission.

37:00.000 --> 37:02.240
But Luwei doesn't like
this kind of gathering.

37:02.320 --> 37:03.160
I don't think she'd come.

37:05.000 --> 37:08.240
Ms. Diemeng,
didn't you say you met up with Luwei?

37:08.320 --> 37:11.120
Is she afraid to meet with us,
her friends?

37:11.320 --> 37:12.480
Unless what you said was...

37:13.320 --> 37:16.600
Fine, I'll go talk to Luwei.

37:17.320 --> 37:18.560
I'm sure she'll do me this favor.

37:20.760 --> 37:24.280
Great, it's decided then.
Let's pick a time.

37:29.680 --> 37:32.480
You think I don't know
this is all your doing?

37:34.840 --> 37:36.720
Let's see who will be disgraced then.

37:38.440 --> 37:44.000
But, the way Luwei is...
I think I can only...

38:16.320 --> 38:18.480
Answer the phone for me. I'm driving.

38:19.040 --> 38:22.240
Sure. Is it a telemarketer?

38:22.960 --> 38:25.040
- Hello?
- It's my mom.

38:33.360 --> 38:36.280
Hi, Professor! Um, Xiao Nai is driving.

38:36.360 --> 38:39.080
I answered the phone for him. Here he is.

38:42.360 --> 38:43.480
SPEAKERPHONE

38:45.600 --> 38:48.080
Mom, you have reception now?

38:48.400 --> 38:50.400
Yes, we just got off the mountain.

38:51.400 --> 38:52.720
The girl...

38:52.800 --> 38:56.640
- You charmed is with you?
- Yes, she's interning at my company.

38:57.040 --> 38:59.440
We just got off work. I'm taking her home.

39:00.240 --> 39:03.000
I was caught off guard.

39:03.120 --> 39:04.240
I didn't talk to her much,

39:04.320 --> 39:06.840
but she sounds like a good girl.

39:06.920 --> 39:08.200
Don't take advantage of her.

39:09.520 --> 39:10.440
It depends.

39:11.000 --> 39:12.520
What depends?

39:12.920 --> 39:15.640
If you do, you have to be responsible.

39:20.440 --> 39:22.800
Mom, I'm on speakerphone.

39:30.360 --> 39:32.360
Xiao Nai, Ms. Bei Weiwei,

39:32.440 --> 39:34.760
come visit us anytime. Bye now.

39:44.960 --> 39:49.120
You took one call
and made all three people hate you.

39:50.840 --> 39:54.040
You're too kind.
I've always been gifted in this regard.

39:55.160 --> 39:57.480
It's not a compliment. Also,

39:58.280 --> 40:00.360
why don't your calls ever show
the the contact name?

40:01.680 --> 40:02.640
I recognize the numbers.

40:41.000 --> 40:43.320
As my mother said,
"take advantage of you."

41:20.720 --> 41:23.440
Your soot-face look is most unexpected.

41:23.520 --> 41:27.720
- It startled me.
- What soot-face? It's black facial mask.

41:28.280 --> 41:31.520
Weiwei, I want to die.

41:32.160 --> 41:33.320
I just put it on.

41:33.400 --> 41:35.560
I want it to absorb
all of today's dark energy.

41:36.640 --> 41:38.720
Dark energy? What's wrong?

41:39.440 --> 41:41.600
The young master's girlfriends came today.

41:41.680 --> 41:42.960
That was an eye-opener for me.

41:44.000 --> 41:46.400
- Girlfriends?
- It's a gang of girls.

41:46.480 --> 41:47.920
They look the same and dress the same.

41:48.240 --> 41:49.560
But that's not the point.

41:49.640 --> 41:53.680
The point is, I'm an exceptional intern,

41:53.760 --> 41:56.320
yet they bossed me around like a maid.

41:56.400 --> 41:58.160
They spilled coffee on my white sneaker.

41:58.240 --> 41:59.600
I washed it all night,
but it's still stained.

42:00.600 --> 42:02.160
I want to die!

42:02.240 --> 42:05.360
Okay. Erxi, poor thing.

42:05.440 --> 42:07.120
Here, I'll give you a massage.
Calm down.

42:07.200 --> 42:09.520
- Here.
- Here?

42:10.520 --> 42:11.680
It feels great.

42:13.520 --> 42:16.560
By the way, Weiwei,
I almost forgot to tell you

42:16.640 --> 42:18.080
something very important.

42:19.800 --> 42:22.200
After slaving away for days on end,

42:22.520 --> 42:24.040
Huantian Xidi's blacksmithing

42:24.120 --> 42:26.320
has at last made the grade.

42:26.960 --> 42:29.800
This is a joyous event
that all should celebrate!

42:30.640 --> 42:31.920
This is great!

42:32.000 --> 42:33.920
No more harsh squealing from you,

42:34.000 --> 42:37.360
and no more being summoned
to help you advance the grade.

42:39.600 --> 42:43.960
Um, the sword I'm making
is still missing a material.

42:44.640 --> 42:46.480
I can't beat the boss.

42:46.560 --> 42:48.160
Weiwei.

42:48.240 --> 42:51.440
Take pity on the emotional trauma
I suffered today.

42:52.520 --> 42:53.360
Get the laptop.

45:29.520 --> 45:31.960
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
